{
  "id": "2666957009_1",
  "title": "杨靖宇牺牲后笔记本被日伪军警掳走，尘封85年的档案首次公布",
  "content": "<div class=\"rich_media_content js_underline_content defaultNoSetting\" id=\"js_content\">\n <section data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\n   <strong>\n    <span style='font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;text-indent: 2em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;'>\n     7月3日上午，尘封八十五载的杨靖宇笔记本档案在吉林省通化市档案馆首次公布。\n    </span>\n   </strong>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <br/>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"434\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"519473352\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/q6I0bRibYUsIhVNgoSQ9e4CicTv7icqWQticd5wJsn1mlpHNR02pMj6QicfmnsZqObaePpFnN3KibtR4zYRfYoDiad7zg/640?wx_fmt=other&amp;from=appmsg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style='font-family: \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, \"system-ui\", \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;white-space: normal;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;height: auto;' type=\"block\"/>\n </section>\n <p>\n  <br/>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   这份编号“通省警特秘第一五三七号”的机密文件，是1940年3月16日伪通化省警务厅长岸谷隆一郎发给柳河县警务科长的杨靖宇笔记本译文。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <br/>\n </p>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <strong>\n   <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n    1940年2月23日，杨靖宇血洒濛江（今靖宇县），壮烈殉国。\n   </span>\n  </strong>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <strong>\n   <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </strong>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <strong>\n   <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n    残暴的敌人解剖了杨靖宇的遗体，却震惊地发现：他的胃里没有一粒粮食，只有一团团枯草、树皮和棉絮。\n   </span>\n  </strong>\n </section>\n <p>\n  <br/>\n </p>\n <section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n  <section>\n   <iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FxrFYciaHL08Duvdc3vqLnIuNkQlv58xkhuY9yHx1I7G7YYQDJPHaP8tSX7gC1PNGLIiaJPqPibhLvRr5MMcS1zdeA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_4055542276561567744\" data-ratio=\"0.7530864197530864\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_4055542276561567744\" data-vidtype=\"5\" data-w=\"488\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border-radius: 4px;\">\n   </iframe>\n  </section>\n </section>\n <p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <br/>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 18px;\">\n   <strong>\n    <strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-indent: 34px;white-space: normal;\">\n     杨靖宇\n    </strong>\n    随身携带的笔记本落入敌手，其内容被紧急译成日文，成为日伪军“讨伐”抗联的情报。\n   </strong>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <br/>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-indent: 34px;font-size: 18px;\">\n   伪满政权灭亡之际，伪通化省公署、警务厅及其所辖各县公署、警察署开始大规模焚烧档案，大量的政务、警务活动档案被其销毁，这件文档混杂在未被彻底销毁的伪柳河县警务科警察工资表、请假条等残余材料中，得以留存至今。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <br/>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 18px;\">\n   <strong>\n    十二页译文，十一个要项，字字千钧。\n   </strong>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style='text-indent: 2em;font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-size: 18px;'>\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style='font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;text-indent: 2em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-size: 18px;'>\n   档案清晰呈现了将军牺牲前数月的思考轨迹。\n   <strong>\n    他详尽分析时局与国际形势\n   </strong>\n   ，\n   <strong>\n    严谨设定部队联络的暗号、旗帜、时间与地点\n   </strong>\n   ，\n   <strong>\n    精确统计兵力、战斗损失、伤员情况及紧缺的装备、弹药、冬装粮食，亲\n   </strong>\n   <strong>\n    笔部署特务队冬季工作计划\n   </strong>\n   。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <section nodeleaf=\"\" style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, \"system-ui\", \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;'>\n  <br/>\n </section>\n <section nodeleaf=\"\" style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, \"system-ui\", \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;'>\n  <img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"834\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"519473348\" data-ratio=\"1.443496801705757\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"469\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/q6I0bRibYUsIhVNgoSQ9e4CicTv7icqWQticFp7QYBxXXCHn24A1n5Wmkfn8eibzfLR9PG97q0vNzKVlXMZV2QBWFdg/640?wx_fmt=other&amp;from=appmsg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto;\" type=\"block\"/>\n </section>\n <section nodeleaf=\"\" style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, \"system-ui\", \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;'>\n  <img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"817\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"519473347\" data-ratio=\"1.4133611691022965\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"479\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/q6I0bRibYUsIhVNgoSQ9e4CicTv7icqWQtic8hviaOiaPRgEHFIoPzWHewGwuws8EEIrV91sabiaOzhuwlemrJ4RDeFTA/640?wx_fmt=other&amp;from=appmsg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto;\" type=\"block\"/>\n </section>\n <section nodeleaf=\"\" style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, \"system-ui\", \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;'>\n  <img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"829\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"519473350\" data-ratio=\"1.4343220338983051\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"472\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/q6I0bRibYUsIhVNgoSQ9e4CicTv7icqWQticB3P99utOkWsuYz7IDUC4Nv9Rwjrhx4g3FWdPIDg0SGb0ljBYAd7G5w/640?wx_fmt=other&amp;from=appmsg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto;\" type=\"block\"/>\n </section>\n <p style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-family: \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, \"system-ui\", \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em;'>\n  <br/>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   这份经由敌手翻译得以意外保存的记录，因其内容的原始性和真实性，成为研究杨靖宇将军和东北抗联历史的极其珍贵的客观史料。档案再现了\n   <strong>\n    杨靖宇将军在极其危险、恶劣的环境下依然艰苦卓绝开展抗日武装斗争的真实情况，为杨靖宇事迹研究及东北抗联史研究提供了新实证。\n   </strong>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <br/>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-align: center;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 20px;color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">\n   <strong>\n    铭记历史\n    <br/>\n   </strong>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-align: center;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 20px;color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">\n   <strong>\n    致敬英雄\n   </strong>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <br/>\n </section>\n <hr style='max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);border-style: solid;border-right-width: 0px;border-bottom-width: 0px;border-left-width: 0px;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.098);transform-origin: 0px 0px 0px;transform: scale(1, 0.5);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;'/>\n <p style='max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;'>\n  <span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n   来源：通化发布、央视新闻\n   <br style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style='max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;'>\n  <span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n   本期编辑：李娜、林帆\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style='max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;'>\n  <img class=\"__bg_gif rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"169\" data-backw=\"574\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/xrFYciaHL08BMq1Er5otH3veEWm0Gm4EcXDCzQM0GqPIQicibBUEVGskz2ElAmhtSqbPxvdIEWBslRSvlficibUDVeg/640?\" data-imgfileid=\"519473354\" data-ratio=\"0.29444444444444445\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"900\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/xrFYciaHL08BMq1Er5otH3veEWm0Gm4EcXDCzQM0GqPIQicibBUEVGskz2ElAmhtSqbPxvdIEWBslRSvlficibUDVeg/640?wx_fmt=gif\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5525px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 1080px !important;\" width=\"auto\"/>\n  <br style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/>\n </p>\n <p style='max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.5525px;text-align: right;margin-bottom: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;'>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">\n   <strong style=\"max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.54px;font-family: 微软雅黑;line-height: 25.6px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 20px;max-width: 100%;background-image: none;background-size: auto;bottom: auto;clear: none;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);height: auto;left: auto;max-height: none;min-height: 0px;min-width: 0px;top: auto;visibility: visible;z-index: auto;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n     <strong style=\"max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.54px;font-size: 18px;line-height: 25.6px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n      <span style=\"font-size: 20px;max-width: 100%;background-color: rgb(234, 6, 13);background-image: none;background-size: auto;bottom: auto;clear: none;height: auto;left: auto;max-height: none;min-height: 0px;min-width: 0px;top: auto;visibility: visible;z-index: auto;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n       <strong style=\"max-width: 100%;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.54px;line-height: 25.6px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n        <span style=\"font-size: 20px;max-width: 100%;background-color: rgb(234, 6, 13);background-image: none;background-size: auto;bottom: auto;clear: none;height: auto;left: auto;max-height: none;min-height: 0px;min-width: 0px;top: auto;visibility: visible;z-index: auto;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n         铭记历史，致敬英雄↓\n         <strong style=\"max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.54px;line-height: 25.6px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n          <span style=\"max-width: 100%;background-image: none;background-size: auto;bottom: auto;clear: none;height: auto;left: auto;max-height: none;min-height: 0px;min-width: 0px;top: auto;visibility: visible;z-index: auto;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n           <strong style=\"max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.54px;line-height: 25.6px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n            <strong style=\"max-width: 100%;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.54px;line-height: 25.6px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n             <span style=\"max-width: 100%;background-color: rgb(234, 6, 13);background-image: none;background-size: auto;bottom: auto;clear: none;height: auto;left: auto;max-height: none;min-height: 0px;min-width: 0px;top: auto;visibility: visible;z-index: auto;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n              ↓\n             </span>\n            </strong>\n           </strong>\n          </span>\n         </strong>\n        </span>\n       </strong>\n       <strong style=\"max-width: 100%;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.54px;line-height: 25.6px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n        <span style=\"font-size: 20px;max-width: 100%;background-color: rgb(234, 6, 13);background-image: none;background-size: auto;bottom: auto;clear: none;height: auto;left: auto;max-height: none;min-height: 0px;min-width: 0px;top: auto;visibility: visible;z-index: auto;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n         ↓\n        </span>\n       </strong>\n      </span>\n     </strong>\n    </span>\n   </strong>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"display: none;\">\n  <mp-style-type data-valu